      <div class="msgContentFrame">Lets get these class boards going.  <br /> <br />What skills from other classes are you looking forward to getting on your lancer.  <br /> <br />I think Second wind is going to be a must for soloing, and Blindside is going to be huge for group play. Bloodbath could also be pretty cool for solo play.  <br /> <br /> <br />Just wondering what other combos people are interested in? <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/971172.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
