anger ability). <br /> <br />At certain lvl, Cure 1 will cure you less for what you take, thats a total waste. <br /> <br />You didnt put second wind, who is enhanced by your Rank, there is also the second wind II. <br />Stoneskin, 12MP for only a hit, and you didnt absorb completely the hit. <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 18th 2010  5:00pm by Memoris </span></i></div>
